S|Cross-Venture Signal|**Both ventures share the same root problem: the anl stack exists structurally (tables defined, Supabase connected) but is not operational.** This is not a vtr-specific failure — it's an infrastructure gap. The YVON OS has a dashboard layer (`app/screens/anl/`) and database tables but no active data ingestion between them. For Marcus: this means all dashboards showing zeros are *accurate* — the data literally isn't there — not a rendering bug. The fix is pl engineering, not dashboard fixes. // T